1. HR+/HER2-: CDK4/6 inhibitor + AI or fulvestrant — standard

2. HER2+: trastuzumab + pertuzumab + taxane (CLEOPATRA); subsequent: T-DXd (trastuzumab deruxtecan — DESTINY-Breast03 superior), T-DM1, tucatinib + capecitabine

